        <h3>We Assess and Make You an Offer</h3>
        <p>We'll evaluate the property — sometimes in person, sometimes remotely — and make you a real cash offer within 24 hours. The number is based on actual Wichita market comps and the condition of the home. We'll walk you through how we got there.</p>
      </div>
